{"tid":1930991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到攬炒巴見到］再眾籌全球登報號召全世界制裁中國","createTime":"2020-03-18T02:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T06:02:24.000Z","uid":245820,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"67e9af7770247af9e263ca4b9846b1e525145ec0","tid":1930991,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:31:15.000Z","msg":"呢兩個月每次行動都好少人<br />\n因為大家都怕出街惹到病毒<br />\n但咁唔代表香港人已經麻木<br />\n已經放棄喺前線嘅手足！<br />\n<br />\n而家全世界被Chinese Virus搞到雞毛鴨血<br />\n各國民間必定有一定程度仇中情緒<br />\n呢個正正係我哋確立香港人身份嘅大好機會！<br />\n話俾全世界人聽 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HONG KONG IS NOT CHINA!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除咗呼籲美國朋友喺census填HongKonger<br />\n我哋係咪應該好似上年6月咁眾籌全球登報<br />\n同全世界講清楚中國係世界公敵<br />\n香港人一直勇於反抗中國<br />\n企喺普世價值一邊<br />\n呼籲西方自由世界繼續<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">STAND WITH HONG KONG!</span></span><br />\n呢個時勢要做到上年6月咁嘅規模<br />\n只有攬炒巴有咁嘅號召力<br />\n認同嘅一齊推到攬炒巴見到！"},{"pid":"52d2f1bc296db5b2e670829da2fb528ea6287d20","tid":1930991,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e543c414b5295cf847071373148d37c84d57d1","tid":1930991,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:32:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0769d1b6e72b6a74f0c8cd092b443203a635436","tid":1930991,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:35:58.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"c7b2df0da4f02e3f4fcabfdeb832776d702b7914","tid":1930991,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:36:30.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7f9eb5e85f2a8a1574aa833de81ff4e582ef859b","tid":1930991,"uid":34881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"1e30e36c279896a467e36a881cfe924a33beeb59","tid":1930991,"uid":245820,"like":0,"dislike":0,